{
  "page": "Hoare Castle",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Hoare Castle</b> was a castle on <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Wyk\" title=\"Great Wyk\">Great Wyk</a> and one of the seats of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Hoare\" title=\"House Hoare\">House Hoare</a> when they ruled as <a href=\"/index.php/Kings_of_the_Iron_Islands\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Kings of the Iron Islands\">Kings of the Iron Islands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hoare_Castle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>House Hoare was originally from <a href=\"/index.php/Orkmont\" title=\"Orkmont\">Orkmont</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown when Hoare Castle was built on Great Wyk.\n</p><p>King <a href=\"/index.php/Harmund_III_Hoare\" title=\"Harmund III Hoare\">Harmund III Hoare</a> was overthrown by the priests of the <a href=\"/index.php/Drowned_God\" title=\"Drowned God\">Drowned God</a>, who imprisoned the king in Hoare Castle, crowned his brother, <a href=\"/index.php/Hagon_Hoare\" title=\"Hagon Hoare\">Hagon</a>, and mutilated their mother, Dowager Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Lelia_Lannister\" title=\"Lelia Lannister\">Lelia Lannister</a>. In retaliation, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Lannister\" title=\"House Lannister\">House Lannister</a> invaded the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>. The Lannister commander, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Aubrey_Crakehall\" title=\"Aubrey Crakehall\">Aubrey Crakehall</a>, defeated King Hagon the Heartless, gave the <a href=\"/index.php/Gift_of_mercy\" title=\"Gift of mercy\">gift of mercy</a> to Harmund in the dungeon, and ordered that the castle be razed to the ground.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Hoare_Castle&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_iron_islands:_the_black_blood.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Iron Islands: The Black Blood.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">The Citadel. Heraldry:  <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/3/\">Houses on the Iron Islands</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table cellspacing=\"0\" class=\"navbox\" style=\"border-spacing: